publicwhip.spmotion: *S2M-503 Margaret Jamieson: British Baker of the Year - Brownings the Bakers Kilmarnock-That the Parliament congratulates Brownings the Bakers, Kilmarnock in being the first Scottish company to be awarded the British Baker of the Year award.
